no good, so we steered clear.</i>

75
00:03:16,930 --> 00:03:20,162
In the basement, reason two
the Couple settled at The Nave.

76
00:03:20,901 --> 00:03:22,062
<i>The vault.</i>

77
00:03:22,469 --> 00:03:24,404
