173
00:08:33,847 --> 00:08:37,716
We pull the fire alarm, blend into
the emotional pandemonium, exit.

174
00:08:38,385 --> 00:08:40,650
With a nod to <i>Fantastic
Beasts.</i> One problem.

175
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:43,315
